People,can,retrieve,data,from,TreasuryDirect,gov,programmatically,using,RESTful,APIs,The,Treasury,Securities,API,lets,users,get,information,on,announced,securities,auctioned,securities,particular,types,of,securities,or,specific,individual,securities,The,Debt,API,lets,users,get,the,most,recent,debt,data,or,the,debt,data,for,a,given,date,API,users,can,also,perform,searches,for,securities,and,debt,data